snippet.title: Making of "A (W)hole lot of Colors" (Brackeys Gamejam 2020.1)
snippet.description:
This time, I made a game in just 3 days! I joined the Brackeys game jam.
Play the game for free here: https://jellever.itch.io/a-whole-lot-of-colors
If you liked this video, be sure to subscribe!
-----------------------------
Music by: https://incompetech.filmmusic.io
------------------------------

Personal website: http://www.jellever.be
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jellevermandere/
And loads more! Just google me ;)
